labelmgr.description: Label manager module configuration root node.

label-range.description:
The configuration info about label-range. The range <global-min,global-max> is the total range of labels, label range for each protocol must be in the global label range.
According to the agreement on the label range to be divided, each label ranges can not overlap. The configuration of label range for kompella is optional,  the range is invalid representing not support kompella label when no configuration at the first time, and the range <kompella-min,kompella-max> can not exceed the maximum 65536 when configuration. Label range changes will take effect at the next reload.

global.description: The range of global label. Its value is not constant, may be different for each product. In some products it is 16-1048575.

static.description: The range of static label. Its value is not constant, may be different for each product. In some products it is 16-16383.

ldp.description: The range of LDP label. Its value is not constant, may be different for each product. In some products it is 16384-81919.

pwe3.description: The range of PWE3 label. Its value is not constant, may be different for each product. In some products it is 81920-147455.

rsvp.description: The range of RSVP label. Its value is not constant, may be different for each product. In some products it is 147456-212991.

bgp.description: The range of BGP label. Its value is not constant, may be different for each product. In some products it is 212992-622591.

bgpv6.description: The range of BGPv6 label. Its value is not constant, may be different for each product. In some products it is 622592-1032191.

kompella.description: Kompella label range is optional, if you configure the range of other labels not configuring kompella label range at the first time, kompella label range is invalid. If the entire label-range is not set, kompella use the default range. The default range is different for each product, and in some products it is 1032192-1048575.

ac.description: Ac label range is optional, if you configure the range of other labels not configuring Ac label range at the first time, Ac label range is invalid. If the entire label-range is not set, Ac label range use the default range. The default range is different for each product.

min.description: The minimum of Ac label range.

max.description: The maximum of Ac label range.

srgb.description: SRGB label range is optional, if you configure the range of other labels not configuring SRGB label range at the first time, SRGB label range is invalid. If the entire label-range is not set, SRGB use the default range.The default range is different for each product.

min.description: The minimum of SRGB label range.

max.description: The maximum of SRGB label range.

srlb.description: SRLB label range is optional, if you configure the range of other labels not configuring SRLB label range at the first time, SRLB label range is invalid. If the entire label-range is not set, SRLB use the default range. The default range is different for each product.

min.description: The minimum of SRLB label range.

max.description: The maximum of SRLB label range.

static-label-range.description: Configure some segments for static label range.

min.description: The minimum of the static label range.

max.description: The maximum of the static label range.

label-reservation.description: Configure label reservation number for each protocol.

ldp.description: The reservation number of LDP label.

pwe3.description: The reservation number of PWE3 label.

rsvp.description: The reservation number of RSVP label.

bgp.description: The reservation number of BGP label.

bgpv6.description: The reservation number of BGPV6 label.

ac-label.description: The reservation number of AC label.

srlb.description: The reservation number of SRLB label.

auto-relocalization.description: Control capability of automatic relocalization for label resource.

enable.description:
The capability of automatic relocalization for label resource.
ENABLE    :    1
DISABLE :      2

forbidden-label-range.description: Configure some segments for forbidden label range.

min.description: The minimum of the forbidden label range.

max.description: The maximum of the forbidden label range.

min.description: The minimum of SRGB label range.

max.description: The maximum of SRGB label range.

min.description: The minimum of BIER label range.

max.description: The maximum of BIER label range.
